CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 30, 1958, pg. A15, reads: "Mrs. Jamerson Entertains - Mrs. J. W. Jamerson of Savannah, Ga., the former Mrs. Harriet Lewis of Pittsburgh, entertained close friends in her former hometown during a stay in Steel City. With her was her daughter, Jayne, left.  Mrs. Jamerson returns to Savannah this week. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Jayne Lewis Williams, and Harriet Lewis Jamerson wearing lace suit and brooch with eyeglasses, standing in Greene Hearth
